data.title: OAESA - Ohio Association of Elementary School Administrators
data.text:
Back

Reward and develop your essential office staff!

This practical, hands-on, two-day conference is designed to help your secretary—and your school—go to the next level with topics from time management and organization, to technology skills, office management, and legal updates. The event will also include interactive networking sessions, buffet lunches, and a hospitality hour—with giveaways!

And, don't miss inspirational, reflective, and humorous keynotes by Jamie Meade (Battle for Kids), Amber Miskovich (The Wonder Within), and Stevie Ray (Speaker and comedian)!

Click here to view the agenda for the Secretaries Conference.

Click here to access the hotel room block at a discounted rate by November 11.
